==== Data Safety Monitoring Board

An independent DSMB will review safety data every 6 months and conduct interim efficacy analysis at 50% enrollment.
*Stopping Rules*
    - Significantly higher rate of serious adverse events in intervention arm
    - Significantly higher rate of disease worsening in intervention arm
    - Clear evidence of benefit or futility at interim analysis (O'Brien-Fleming boundaries)

